      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including large dents, pervasive scratches, and visible rust patches on several panels. Mechanically, the car requires substantial repairs; it currently struggles to start and has several known leaks and suspension issues. The interior shows heavy wear, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest significant time and resources to bring this vehicle back to a drivable state.",
