    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of life left? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a reliable choice for anyone seeking practical transportation at a great value. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a solid car that's still got plenty of character and utility!",
