    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and is officially ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs smoothly, and honestly still looks fantastic inside and out. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and updated suspension bushings to maintain optimal geometry under load. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. A mechanically sound example that balances raw performance with refined German engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
