      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of luxury and reliability with this meticulously maintained vehicle. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor, age-appropriate imperfections that do not detract from its striking presence on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows minimal wear, while all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in superb health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with all service records available for your review. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the tires have ample tread remaining for many miles of confident driving. This is a turn-key vehicle for a buyer who values a car that has been treated with genuine care and professional attention to detail.",
      "price": 38500.0,
